high_descs: Turn and go left and then left again and stand in front of the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the pan up from the counter.
Move left and turn to face the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn on the water and then turn it off and pick up the pan.
Turn and go the the right and stand at the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the pan down on the counter to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen counter right of the sink
Pick up the dirty square pan from the counter
Move slightly left then turn to face the kitchen sink
Wash the pan under the water in the sink then remove it
Turn around, walk a few feet, then turn left toward the counter right of the stove
Put the pan down on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned pan on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up a dirty pan on the counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and take the pan out of the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter by the stove.
Put the pan on the counter by the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed pan by the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the dirty pan on the counter.
Turn left, bring the pan to the sink.
Clean the pan in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned pan to the counter right of the stove.
Put the cleaned pan on the counter right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the counter right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the pan next to the stove.
Move left a few feet to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and move to the counter on the right of the stove.
With the handle facing the wall, put the pan on the counter between the stove and the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on counter next to the toaster.
